Our Casa-Club, completely renovated in 1995, consists of Reception-Concierge, cafeteria area, two lounges-restaurants, lounge and games area, and large terraces.
        On the first floor are offices, meeting rooms, children\'s room and billiards room. The newest part of the building consists of the club room, changing rooms with sauna and gym;
        On the upper floor, the TV room and a multipurpose area with large terraces overlooking the golf course, suitable for various activities, from cafeteria to exhibition hall.
